{"tid":1875163,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"假設疫症蔓延到半年後，中共話成功研發到疫苗 大家又敢唔敢打？","createTime":"2020-02-11T15:11:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-12T08:25:36.000Z","uid":67348,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"14fa455c4e231952bf6f1c5ea4ea17b0955ac36d","tid":1875163,"uid":67348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T15:11:13.000Z","msg":"假設個疫症蔓延多半年（或者更長嘅時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />），而到時全國+全世界都死傷無數。<br />\n呢個時候，中共話成功研製到對付武漢肺炎病毒嘅疫苗，宣佈埋證實咗好多支那人打完疫苗 成功痊愈（或者防感染）<br />\n大家覺得香港人到時會唔會打？而大家本人又敢唔敢打？如果唔打 就要繼續冒住隨時中肺炎嘅風險<br />\n我覺得到時個心情會矛盾<br />\n第一 會諗隻疫苗係咪真係有效 支那製造嘅野會唔會打完仲衰過無打？<br />\n第二 我會覺得隻疫苗會唔會有類似監控人嘅功能<br />\n假設打完疫苗真係防到病毒 但有機會俾人監控一世 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔知大家點睇？"},{"pid":"a0ca593bcdce7248d5f2a8ddebcec641a52e3281","tid":1875163,"uid":67348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T15:12:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"458816ef633746e7e0a69d073d4c531e7bcb999e","tid":1875163,"uid":67348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T15:14:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c39fbb40f7078d9e0d55f39509c6c78d9f52b0ab","tid":1875163,"uid":156121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T15:16:14.000Z","msg":"冇用<br />\n過多幾代支野又冇用"},{"pid":"de49fa7517a10346f92e647043cf8728a37c59c6","tid":1875163,"uid":249705,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T15:16:26.000Z","msg":"點解你覺得支那會快過美國研發到疫苗?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cd599daaec42413160b4e06c96bb163bdaa31ac","tid":1875163,"uid":67348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T15:16:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6a7e25aee63ebf79d16d3108f5889baa7e8eab88","tid":1875163,"uid":67348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"de49fa751